$ IT Service Management
@ ITSM

ITSM is concerned with activities needed for IT:
  • Design
  • Planning
  • Delivering
  • Operating
  • Controlling

{ Service desk #itsm-service-desk

  A primary function within ITSM is the ~service desk~ (see ITIL). The service desk provides a *single point of contact* (SPOC) for service users and
  service providers (the latter typically working in IT).

}
